n William Scott) mom (Jennifer Coolidge). These lifelong friends have come home to reminisce about -- and become inspired by -- their former teen selves.'),('MV003752050000','Dear Santa','2011','Crystal, a rich party girl, finds a little girl\'s letter to Santa asking for a new mother, and she vows to win over the father and daughter before the holidays.'),('MV003756120000','The Lucky One','2012','U.S. Marine Sgt. Logan Thibault (Zac Efron) returns home from his third tour of duty in Iraq with the one thing he believes kept him alive: a photograph of a woman he doesn\'t even know. He learns the woman\'s name is Beth (Taylor Schilling) and goes to meet her, eventually taking a job at her family-run kennel. Though Beth is full of mistrust and leads a complicated life, a romance blooms, giving Logan hope that Beth could become more than just his good-luck charm.'),('MV003845400000','Las Dos Vidas de Andrés Rabadán','2008','Once años después de descarrilar tres trenes y matar a su padre con una ballesta, un hombre planea escapar del psiquiátrico penitenciario en el que se encuentra encerrado.'),('MV003857660000','The Watch','2012','In Glenview, Ohio, four pals -- Evan (Ben Stiller), Bob (Vince Vaughn), Franklin (Jonah Hill) and Jamarcus (Richard Ayoade) -- form a neighborhood watch group. Armed with flashlights, walkie-talkies and spiffy new jackets, the guys try to take their mission seriously, even if they spend a little time goofing off now and then. But when they discover aliens living among them, and no one believes their story, they learn that they have to kick things up a notch to save the world from annihilation.'),('MV003867280000','Sparkle','2012','In 1968, girl groups and the Motown sound are sweeping the nation. Despite their mother\'s (Whitney Houston) misgivings, talented sisters Delores (Tika Sumpter), Sister (Carmen Ejogo) and Sparkle (Jordin Sparks) are taking Detroit by storm, and their dreams are even bigger. Their ambitious manager (Derek Luke) will 